fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(18, 6))

for n in range(0,20,2):
    start =100*n
    stop = 100*(n+1)
    ax.plot(df.ch1[start:stop], marker='s', color='blue', label='input')
    ax.plot(df.ch1[stop:2*stop], marker='x', color='red', label='label')
